	</li>
      </ul>
    </objectives>
    <page>
      <exercise workspace="1in">
	<p>
	  Determine whether the equation <m>2x + 3yx = 3xy + 7y - 4</m> is linear.
	  If the equation is linear, put it standard form.
	  Otherwise, explain why the equation is not linear.
	</p>
      </exercise>

      <exercise workspace="1in">
	<p>
	  Determine whether the equation <m>2(x - 2)^2 + y = 3x</m> is linear.
	  If the equation is linear, put it standard form.
	  Otherwise, explain why the equation is not linear.
	</p>
      </exercise>
    </page>
